text.tspan: Monthly confirmed cases of influenza B Yamagata
This shows the number of cases that were confirmed to be of the Yamagata lineage of influenza B virus. Only
a fraction of potential cases of influenza are tested by labs to confirm whether they have influenza and to
identify their strain. The level of testing may vary between countries and over time.
Data source: FluNet by the World Health Organization (2023)
